data.description:
Welcome home to this adorable beach bungalow in Paradise Cove! You're greeted a large front porch with a swing. Walk in to the large living space featuring tongue and groove shiplap on the vaulted ceiling with a wood beam, board and batten wainscoting all around with an electronic fireplace featuring a cedar mantle. The wet bar & kitchen feature custom hardwood cabinets, marble counters and backsplashes. There is wood look tile throughout with engineered hardwoods in all 3 bedrooms. Out back you will find a covered patio, a large seating area overlooking the backyard and a brand new custom outdoor shower. 
Other features include: a Rinnai tankless gas hot water heater, gas stove, custom hurricane shutters, a new roof in 2021, newer HVAC, a water softener with whole house filtration system and a reverse osmosis system at the sink, real barn wood at breakfast bar, built in storage in the garage, the home is preplumbed for a laundry sink and is prewired for a generator hook up.
